  어제의 야구 결과는?</a></h2>
  <h2><a href="https://search.naver.com/search.naver?where=nexearch&sm=top_hty&fbm=1&ie=utf8&query=%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%95%BC%EA%B5%AC" target="_blank" title="선수 순위">
